title: Navigate forwards to a spinbutton
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate forwards from here' link, navigate to the 'Adults' spinbutton.

title: Navigate backwards to a spinbutton
instructions: Starting at the 'Navigate backwards from here' link, navigate to the 'Adults' spinbutton.

title: Request information about a spinbutton
instructions: Starting at the 'Adults' spinbutton, read information about the spinbutton.

title: Request information about an invalid value in a spinbutton
instructions: Starting at the 'Adults' spinbutton (invalid value 9), read information about the spinbutton.
assertions: roleSpinbutton nameAdults value9 isInvalid minimumValue1 maximumValue8 errorMessage

title: Increment a spinbutton by one step
instructions: Starting at the 'Adults' spinbutton (value 1), set its value to 2.

title: Decrement a spinbutton by one step
instructions: Starting at the 'Adults' spinbutton (value 2), set its value to 1.

title: Decrement a spinbutton to the minimum value (Home)
instructions: Starting at the 'Adults' spinbutton (value 2), set its value to 1 (minimum).

title: Increment a spinbutton to the maximum value (End)
instructions: Starting at the 'Adults' spinbutton (value 1), set its value to 8 (maximum).
